The paper proposes two regularization methods for deep neural networks, which are evaluated on benchmark datasets and time series modeling tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
